==English==

===Pronunciation===
*kărˈə-văn, /ˈkærəvæn/, /"k{r@v{n/

===Noun===
'''caravan''' (plural: [[caravans]])

# a [[convoy]] or procession of travelers and [[pack animal]]s, especially [[camel]]s crossing a [[desert]].
# (British, Aus) a furnished vehicle [[tow]]ed behind a car etc and used as a dwelling when stationary.

====Synonyms====
*(British) [[travel trailer]] (2)
*(''US'') [[trailer]] (2)
*(''US'') [[camper]] (2)
*(''US'') [[motor home]] (2)
*(''US'') [[recreational vehicle]]


